preparepkg.pl 13.37 (120201)

Usage: preparepkg.pl [options] package_name.txz

Prepares the current and all subdirectories for makepkg by creating
slack-desc, slack-required and gzipping any uncompressed man pages. 
Dependencies are automatically determined and written to slack-required. 

options: -r, --required       Generate slack-required.
         -h, --help           Display usage.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
mkslack-required.pl 13.37 (120201)

Usage: mkslack-required.pl

Run from package root dir. Automatically determines dependencies
of package and writes them to install/slack-required

------------------------------------------------------------------------
lsdeps.pl 13.37 (120202)

Usage: lsdeps.pl package_name
       e.g lsdeps.pl xchat

Lists dependencies for an installed package.



